	* modules/irc-channel/chmanagement.c: fixed bugs again - on MODE now.

Tue Sep 19 2006 Andriy Gritsenko <andrej@rep.kiev.ua>
	* modules/irc-channel/irc-channel.c: fixed bugs on netjoin and on
	  nick change.

